---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import heroCoreGraphic from "@/assets/hero-core-graphic.png";
---

<!-- Hero Section -->
<main class="py-20 md:py-32 bg-navy relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Animated background elements -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none">
    <div class="absolute top-10 left-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-blue/10 rounded-full blur-3xl animate-float"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-10 right-1/4 w-80 h-80 bg-yellow/10 rounded-full blur-3xl animate-float delay-200"></div>
    <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-10 w-64 h-64 bg-green/10 rounded-full blur-3xl animate-float delay-400"></div>
  </div>

  <!-- Gradient overlay -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-navy via-transparent to-navy pointer-events-none"></div>

  <div class="text-center max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 relative z-10">
    <p class="text-sm md:text-base font-bold text-yellow tracking-widest uppercase mb-6 animate-fade-in-up">
      IF YOU'RE NOT DOING THIS IN 2026 THEN YOU'RE FALLING BEHIND...
    </p>
    <h1
      class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl xl:text-6xl font-bold lg:tracking-tight xl:tracking-tighter text-white animate-fade-in-up delay-100">
      Every Business NOT Using AI to Enhance Performance is Losing Profitability by the Minute
    </h1>
    <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl mt-6 text-yellow font-semibold italic animate-fade-in-up delay-200">
      Eliminate Friction and Accelerate Revenue Using Our Dedicated Fractional AI Growth Team
    </p>

    <div class="mt-10 mb-8 animate-fade-in-up delay-300">
      <Image
        src={heroCoreGraphic}
        alt="HumTech Core - ROI Delivery, AI Strategy, Training, Sales Psychology, Implementation"
        class="mx-auto max-w-3xl w-full"
        widths={[400, 768, 1024]}
        sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px"
      />
    </div>

    <p class="text-lg text-white/70 animate-fade-in-up delay-400">
      Performance Based Billing With Guaranteed ROI Commitments
    </p>
  </div>
</main>

<!-- Assessment Measures Section -->
<section class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-navy border-t border-white/10 relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Subtle background pattern -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-30 pointer-events-none">
    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-1/2 h-full bg-gradient-to-l from-blue/5 to-transparent"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 relative z-10">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
        This Assessment Measures Your "Engagement Latency"
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-yellow font-semibold">
        These results give insights to improve:
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <div class="group p-6 rounded-xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 card-hover relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-yellow/10 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300"></div>
        <div class="relative z-10">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-yellow/30 to-yellow/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
            <span class="text-yellow font-bold text-xl">1</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-white/80">
            Your proportion of new business lost to competitors due to engagement method and response time
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="group p-6 rounded-xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 card-hover relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-yellow/10 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300"></div>
        <div class="relative z-10">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-yellow/30 to-yellow/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
            <span class="text-yellow font-bold text-xl">2</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-white/80">
            Your 'handling time' vs 'deflection savings' - how much time and money could be saved through hands-free automation
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="group p-6 rounded-xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 card-hover relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-yellow/10 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300"></div>
        <div class="relative z-10">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-yellow/30 to-yellow/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
            <span class="text-yellow font-bold text-xl">3</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-white/80">
            Your overall opportunity cost of current AI strategies and the impact on your team and operational efficiency
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center mt-12">
      <button
        onclick="openAssessmentModal()"
        class="group px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-semibold bg-yellow text-navy shadow-md shadow-black/20 hover:bg-green hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-black/30 transition-all duration-300 inline-flex items-center justify-center cursor-pointer text-lg gap-2">
        Find out exactly where you're losing business
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"></path>
        </svg>
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- 2026 Section -->
<section class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-navy border-t border-white/10">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl xl:text-6xl font-bold lg:tracking-tight text-white mb-6">
      In 2026, Your Business Needs to Keep Up With the Continuously Evolving AI Landscape
    </h2>
    <p class="text-xl text-yellow font-semibold mb-4">
      A dedicated fractional growth team powered by our continuously evolving AI systems
    </p>
    <p class="text-lg text-white/70">
      Performance Based Billing With Guaranteed ROI Committments
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Bottleneck / Problem Section -->
<section class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-navy border-t border-white/10">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
        You know the bottleneck... 50% of inquiries vanish before your sales team gets to them...
      </h2>
      <p class="text-2xl text-yellow font-semibold">
        We faced this exact problem
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Story Block -->
    <div class="prose prose-lg prose-invert max-w-none text-white/70 mb-12">
      <p>
        When starting out, we discovered that only 50% of new enquiries responded to outreach, and just half of them attended booked consultations. Moreover, our small team were constantly drawn into repetitive admin tasks and distractions which took them away from revenue-producing duties.
      </p>
      <p class="text-yellow font-semibold">
        We experimented with countless 'out the box' third-party AI tools (multiple diferent log-ins!), yet conversions actually got worse.
      </p>
      <p>
        So we rolled up our sleeves... and we figured it out on our own.
      </p>
      <p class="font-semibold text-white text-xl">
        One year later, the results speak for themselves...
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center p-8 glass rounded-2xl">
      <p class="text-lg text-white/90">
        In two years, Our marketing agency powered the #1 rated Green Energy Supplier on Trustpilot with 4.9 out of 5.0 Stars with a team of only four people.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Results Stats Section -->
<section class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-navy border-t border-white/10">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6 mb-16">
      <div class="moving-box text-center p-6 bg-gradient-to-br from-yellow/10 to-yellow/5 rounded-xl border border-yellow/20">
        <div class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-yellow">98%</div>
        <div class="text-sm text-white/60 mt-2">client appointment booking rate</div>
      </div>
      <div class="moving-box text-center p-6 bg-gradient-to-br from-yellow/10 to-yellow/5 rounded-xl border border-yellow/20">
        <div class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-yellow">90%+</div>
        <div class="text-sm text-white/60 mt-2">appointment attendance</div>
      </div>
      <div class="moving-box text-center p-6 bg-gradient-to-br from-green/10 to-green/5 rounded-xl border border-green/20">
        <div class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-green">50%</div>
        <div class="text-sm text-white/60 mt-2">increase in revenue</div>
      </div>
      <div class="moving-box text-center p-6 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue/10 to-blue/5 rounded-xl border border-blue/20">
        <div class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-blue">Zero</div>
        <div class="text-sm text-white/60 mt-2">additional team members hired</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- What made the difference -->
    <div class="text-center p-8 glass rounded-2xl">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-yellow">What made the difference?</h3>
      <p class="text-lg text-white/70 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        A team of expert AI, sales and marketing strategists to oversee consultation, implementation, training and ROI target delivery.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Why HumTech Section -->
<section class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-navy border-t border-white/10">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-8">
        Why HumTech?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-white/70 leading-relaxed mb-8">
        Internal employees are focused on keeping up with the directives of the business. They don't have the time to stay plugged into constantly changing AI applications, methods and updates. AI becomes a fast-track for "employee obsolescence" and having to constantly retrain skills.
      </p>
      <p class="text-2xl text-yellow font-semibold mb-8">
        This is where HumTech comes in.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center py-8">
      <span class="text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-bold text-yellow">70%</span>
      <p class="text-xl text-white/70 mt-4">less than hiring just ONE in-house AI director</p>
      <p class="text-lg text-white/50 mt-2 italic">*Plus you get the technical and marketing expertise to properly utilize AI</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- We understand AI Section -->
<section class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-navy border-t border-white/10">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
    <p class="text-2xl text-yellow font-semibold mb-6">
      We understand AI isn't about replacing humans.
    </p>
    <p class="text-xl text-white/80 leading-relaxed">
      It's about freeing your team from repetitive, non-revenue generating tasks so they can focus on delivering an exceptional service to your clients, and keep them longer.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- What You Get Section -->
<section class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-navy border-t border-white/10">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
        What You Get
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-white/80 leading-relaxed">
        Your very own on-demand fractional growth team of specialists with <span class="text-yellow font-semibold">BSc(Hons) and MSc qualifications</span> in computer science and psychology from top 10 universities, and <span class="text-yellow font-semibold">over 15 years experience</span> in building customer acquisition systems.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-8">
      <!-- Citation 1 -->
      <blockquote class="p-8 bg-white/5 rounded-xl border-l-4 border-yellow">
        <p class="text-lg text-white/80 mb-4">
          "AI-human combination results in higher engagement/conversion rates, reduced costs and optimized lead generation. 3x more calls connected, 20% higher meeting hold rate."
        </p>
        <cite class="text-sm text-white/50 not-italic">
          -Koch, S. (2024). A Case Study in AI-Augmented Cold Outreach. The Journal of Business and Artificial Intelligence, 1(1), 1-5
        </cite>
      </blockquote>

      <!-- Citation 2 -->
      <blockquote class="p-8 bg-white/5 rounded-xl border-l-4 border-yellow">
        <p class="text-lg text-white/80 mb-4">
          "AI chat and scheduling bot reduces 'no show rates', reduces administrative burden, improves client satisfaction and increases overall efficiency."
        </p>
        <cite class="text-sm text-white/50 not-italic">
          - Nyako Alhaji Baba et al. (2024). Development of an intelligent chatbot for patient appointment booking system. International Journal of Engineering and Applied Information Systems, 8(10), 55-65
        </cite>
      </blockquote>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Testimonial Section -->
<section class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-navy border-t border-white/10">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="relative p-10 md:p-16 bg-white/5 rounded-2xl border border-white/10">
      <!-- Quote mark decoration -->
      <div class="absolute top-6 left-8 text-yellow/30 text-8xl font-serif leading-none">"</div>

      <blockquote class="relative z-10">
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-white/90 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          "I took the assessment and found we were losing new clients by leaving outreach to our sales team and failing on response time. This was easily verifiable through cold outreach, which identified that almost all initial non-responders had been served by our competitors. We also found how much time our team members were wasting on non-conversions and repetitive tasks."
        </p>
        <cite class="not-italic flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="w-12 h-1 bg-yellow rounded-full"></span>
          <span class="text-lg font-semibold text-yellow">RESG UK</span>
        </cite>
      </blockquote>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
